#- ░ §0§lBusiness§0
§0
§0Levels of gold production continue to decline as portal farmers struggle to combat strict tick- rate regulations and the increasingly dire effects of herd control plugin ‘mustercull’.          »
#- VALEX analysts project that the current situation is unlikely to markedly improve within the next two quarters, citing a low appetite for admin intervention as the main contributor to the current downturn of supply.                §0
§0                      »
#- Gold blocks and ingots have long been a cheap source of beacon foundations and tool construction; however the increasing scarcity of the resource has forced building firms to look elsewhere.
#- ░ §0§lWorld§0
§0
§0An ‘incompatibility of ideals’ is rumoured to be behind a possible leadership change within global superpower §0§oLibertas.§0
§0
§0§othe_jakebob§0 has taken a noticeable absence from the helm for at least    »
#- the past 10 cycles and speculation is growing over the direction that§0
§0§oSintralin§0, the presumed successor, will take the anarcho-capitalist group in future. 
#- ░ §0§lSport§0
§0
§0The 2015 season of New Danzilona Hockey League has opened with a nail-bitingly tense game as a record number of spectators hit the stands to catch a glimpse of the excitement.          » 
#- After three nil-all rounds of the puck going to and fro the game was called to a sudden death, which saw cup defenders Swisston Snow Shovels buckle under pressure and allow rival team Mount Augusta Avalanche a swift victory.§0
§0                        »
#- This means that in the league tables Mount Augusta is now on two points, Swisston one.
#- ░ §0§lHealth§0
§0
§0Exclusive photos smuggled out of the§0
§0§oSeptum Datavault§0 show evidence of serious anthropological consequences to previously player rich areas. §0
§0                        »
#- Whether these unusual declines in settlement activity levels have any relationship to recent reports of an infectious §0§o'Atrophy'§0 disease, remains to be seen.
#- ░ §0§lPolitics§0
§0
§0Long months of groundwork laid with the vision of creating a United Nations of Civcraft drew one step closer to achieving the lofty goal today, as the first glimpse of the proposed United Nations Charter     »
#- was released to the public.§0
§0
§0A key element of the charter involves the formation of a UN Security Council, and the aim of creating a transparent defence force for participating member nations.
